And so, that's what inspires me and it really thrills me as well to see what happened in our rail business, because we did have some big customers that pursued us and we were able to respond. And so, if that continues, then you end up getting some really positive momentum that we would then declare that we have left the bottom and we're moving up in a more upward direction.
Bascome Majors - Susquehanna Financial Group LLLP
