Cleary, the trend over time, Matt, has been that we're seeing more and more leasing activity. The growth of leasing not only by industrial shippers but also by Class I railroads continues to grow. And that's certainly one of the long-term fundamental reasons why we continue to invest in our leasing capabilities to strengthen our business platform.
