Trinity’s rail manufacturing companies serve a wide variety of industries, ranging from energy and chemicals 
to agriculture, automotive, and construction. 









Trinity’s Railcar Leasing and Management Services Group provides railcar leasing and comprehensive rail industry service options that 
enable customers to focus on their core businesses. 








Trinity’s Inland Barge Group manufactures barges used to transport dry and liquid cargo on U.S. inland waterways.









Trinity’s Construction Products Group consists of companies that provide products and services for the construction industry and various infrastructure projects.











Trinity’s Energy Equipment Group includes companies that manufacture a variety of energy-related products. 






 
 
 




 
 
    

 




